   "source": [
    "def getInsolation(number):\n",
    "    days = np.linspace(60, const.days_per_year*24 + 318, 9024)\n",
    "\n",
    "    ins = daily_insolation(number, days)\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.plot(days, ins)\n",
    "\n",
    "    df = pd.DataFrame({'day': days,\n",
    "                    'average_insolation': ins.values})\n",
    "    path = str(number) + \"_\" + \"dailyinsolation.csv\"\n",
    "    df.to_csv(path_or_buf = path, index=False)"
   ]
  },
